ing: 1 (1.12 ounce) package PaceÂ® Taco Seasoning Mix
1 (10.75 ounce) can  Campbell'sÂ® Condensed Tomato Soup
des: "Taco-seasoned ground beef simmered with tomato and rice is topped with salsa, cheese and lettuce for a tortilla chip-dipping meal."
ins:
Cook beef and taco seasoning in skillet until browned. Pour off fat.
Add soup, water and rice. Heat to a boil. Cover and cook over low heat 5 min. or until done.
Top with salsa, cheese and lettuce. Serve with tortilla chips for dipping.
